synopsis: Tan Yun is the young master of the Tan family, a small noble family in Wang Yue Town, but the reincarnation of the Honmong Supreme needs to be stimulated by life and death to awaken, so Tan Yun has been bullied and despised scum for 16 years at first. During the wedding, Tan Yun saw his fiancée cheating on him with the young master of the Situ family and was beaten up, and when he was about to die, he finally awakened to the memories of the Supreme God
